Title: Whatever It Takes
Plot: Based on practically no information and no medical history about a mystery patient sent by the CIA, House is using some unorthodox methods to diagnose and treat him. Meanwhile the remaining candidates are questioning Foreman's judgment.
Writer: Peter Blake, Thomas L. Moran, Thomas L. Moran
GuestStars: Nick Warnock, Amy Dudgeon, Chad Willett, Joel Bissonnette, Holmes Osborne, Michael Michele, Thomas F. Wilson
